author: rjollos
msg: Fixes #469: Fix for failing `BatchModify` unit test cases. The `TicketSystem` implements the `ITicketFieldProvider` interface, and also calls a method of the `ITicketFieldProvider` interface to get a list containing the ticket fields. When the `api.TicketSystem` component is not enabled, the fields provided by that class won't be returned in the call `TicketSystem.get_ticket_fields`. The fields returned by `TicketSystem.get_select_fields` and `TicketSystem.get_radio_fields` are "built-in" ticket fields, which some cases expect to be returned through the call `TicketSystem.get_ticket_fields`.
Thank to Olemis for the patch.
